profile:
ABOUT US
What We Do
Our commercial and residential projects include Driveways, Patios, Curbs, Sidewalks, and Stairs 
Working Together
We offer an end-to-end client experience that includes seamless communication, budgeting, staffing, on-site organization, and solid, quality handiwork every time. 
Why Choose Us?
We are a family-run business that's reliable, economical, and stand by our work!
services:
Residential
We do Custom Driveways, Patios , Stairs to suit any of your concrete needs! - 
Commercial
Specializing in Large pads, Curbs , and Sidewalks to suit any environment! - 
Post-Construction
The last step in any build. This phase includes site cleanup, systems training, final inspections, and move-in coordination. After completion, we have a final walkthrough to ensure your complete satisfaction.

profile:
At Georgifer Concrete you will get the best quality concrete work done for your construction needs. We serve in Brantford and its surrounding regions. All of our workers are highly trained, efficient and reliable for any kind of project. We do residential and commercial contracting as well.

Our Services:

Concrete Work

Parging

Sidewalks

Porch Pads

Home Renovation

Improvements

New Construction

and much more...

Appointments: Contact us today to schedule an appointment and we'll come out and meet with you to discuss your project in further details. 

Business Hours: Monday to Friday 9:00 am to 5:00 pm. If needed, some Saturdays may be available. 

Covid 19: We are following all the health and safety protocals as set by the province to ensure the safety of our customers and employees.
